      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CAWBOURNE OZZY (2) has a strong record this trip with five wins and two placings from eight starts. Scored by a neck last time (19.74) in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Rates on top and should go close. BANDIT LYNNE (1) took the sit on the lead from an outside box but levelled up and drew clear to score (19.77) at this track in a Grade 5 over 350m. Got the money at her only try from this box. Expected to feature again. IRINKA ALANA (8) is a well performed dog and winner of 10 races who was in the minor money last time out at this track (19.76). Boasts two wins from four starts out of this box. Expected to be in this for a long way. BANDIT BLAZE (3) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
